extends _layout

block content

  header( class='intro')
    div( class='intro-body')
      div( class='container')
        div( class='row')
          div( class='col-md-8 col-md-offset-2')
            h1( class='brand-heading' ) Type6.js
            p( class='intro-text') An open source mathematics library written in Javascript.
              br/
              br/ 
              a( href='#about' class='btn btn-circle page-scroll' )
                i( class='fa fa-angle-double-down animated' )

  section( id='about' class='container content-section text-center' )
    div( class='row' )
      div( class='col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2' )
        h2 About
        
        p The main purpose was to provide a comprehensive library for all the projects that require the usual mathematics stuff (vectors, trigonometry, matrices and so on).
        
        p Because of the massive work involved, it's not the complete library yet. I will release the rest as soon as it is ready.

        p Check the 
          a( class='page-scroll' href='#example' ) Examples 
          | section to see how to use Type6.js. There is also a complete 
          a( class='page-scroll' href='#documentation' ) documentation 
          | if you need to go deeper.
        
        p You can help develop Type6.js on 
          a( href='https://github.com/LCluber' target='_blank' ) Github
          |.
        
  section( id='example' class='container content-section text-center' )
    div( class='row' )
      div( class='col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2' )
        h2 Examples
        p Learn how to use Type6.js with those simple experiments

        each category, key in examples
          if category.length
            h3= key
            ul
              each link in category
                li
                  a( href=link.href, target='_self' )=  link.name
                        
  section( id='download' class='container content-section text-center' )
    div( class='row' )
      div( class='col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2' )
        h2 Download Type6.js
        ul( class='list-inline banner-social-buttons' )
          li
            a( href='dist/type6.min.js' class='btn btn-default btn-lg' target='_blank' download='type6.min.js' title='Minified library only') Type6.min.js
          li
            a( href='zip/type6js.zip' class='btn btn-default btn-lg' target='_blank' download='type6js.zip' title='Package with documentation and examples') Type6js.zip 
          li
            a( href='https://github.com/LCluber/Type6.js' class='btn btn-default btn-lg' target='_blank' title='Sources for the entire project')
              i( class='fa fa-github fa-fw' )
              |Clone from Github

  section( id='contact' class='container content-section text-center' )
    div( class='row' )
      div( class='col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2' )
        h2 Contact me
        p Feel free to ask me about my work, give me suggestions, or just to say hi.
        ul( class='list-inline banner-social-buttons' )
          li
            a( href='http://www.lcluber.com/contact.php' class='btn btn-default btn-lg' target='_blank' )
              |lcluber.com
          li
            a( href='https://twitter.com/LCluber' class='btn btn-default btn-lg' target='_blank' )
              i( class='fa fa-twitter fa-fw' ) 
              |Twitter
          li
            a( href='https://github.com/LCluber' class='btn btn-default btn-lg' target='_blank' )
              i( class='fa fa-github fa-fw' ) 
              |Github
